      "severity": "major",
      "reviewer": "chatgpt-codex-connector[bot]",
      "body": "**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Raise the query array limit for data column indices**\n\nThis global cap is still too low for the Fulu debug data-column endpoint: `getDebugDataColumnSidecars` accepts an `indices?: number[]` query array and filters by those indices, while Fulu `DataColumnSidecars` is bounded by `NUMBER_OF_COLUMNS`, which is 128 in the preset (`packages/api/src/beacon/routes/debug.ts:208`, `packages/types/src/fulu/sszTypes.ts:6",
