      "file": "packages/beacon-node/src/api/rest/base.ts",
      "line": 64,
      "severity": "major",
      "reviewer": "spiral-ladder",
      "body": "nit: not sure if this overexplanation is necessary too, don't need to know `qs` implementation details + this lacks context for newer readers who dont know about the breaking change\n\n```suggestion\n/**\n * Cap for array query params, set to the largest array any beacon-API query can carry:\n * a full data-column custody set (`getDebugDataColumnSidecars` `indices`).\n */\nconst QUERY_STRING_ARRAY_LIMIT = NUMBER_OF_COLUMNS;\n```",
